    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kn">import</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nn">java.util.Observable</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">
